Definition: a city in southwestern Pennsylvania where the confluence of the Allegheny River and Monongahela River forms the Ohio River
Example: long an important urban industrial area; site of Carnegie Mellon University and the University of Pittsburgh
Synonyms: city, i, Pennsylvania, p, a, in, southwestern, where, the, confluence, of, Allegheny, River, and, Monongahela, forms, Ohio, long, an, important, urban, industrial, area, site, Carnegie, Mellon, University
Category: noun.location
